	<p><blockquote><span class="smallfont">Quote:</span><hr size="1" />Similarly I do not mind the way I cast cannibalize (or canni 5) - I have the timer right in front of me, no need to switch targets or the like, just hit it when I have a free moment. The same goes for VP, Ancestral Aid and Epic 1.5 clickie - I would go utterly insane if I had to recast VP every 5 seconds, even if it cast instantly. As is I can fire &amp; forget it, no tedium involved.<hr size="1" /></blockquote>These abilities do not take up a spell slot. There is a HUGE difference. I'm not giving up a spell I normally keep memmed to make room for any of these.</p>
	
	
	
