	<!-- message -->
	<p>Throwing out some ideas, assuming its possible to code.  <br />
<br />
How about a buff that gives a piece of your max hp pool to the targeted MT.  <br />
<br />
Works like this shm1 casts on MT shm1 drops (for example) 300hp and gets the buff icon. The MT gets the 300hp added on and 150% to crit rate.  Now shm2-shm5 also hit the MT he now has 1500 more hp and 750% higher crit.  <br />
<br />
The MT would idealy have no buff icon (one if nesecary for coding) the shm would take the buff slot.  Have the spell last at least 60+ min, or until clicked off by the shm. <br />
<br />
For coding purposes have the spell check up similar to bard songs, if the shm clicks off or logs next tick it will drop off the MT.<br />
<br />
The divisions can be adjusted for more or less shm.  Then just set a cap on the total amount that will be effective.</p>
	
	
	
	
	
