	<p>They changed it again. It no longer has a recast time which makes it now useful in group situations. One shaman can now keep it up on several of the tanks in a raid. <br />
<br />
They also changed it from a crit modifier to a 20% 1hb mod, which I'm not so sure about. Not everyone uses 1hb weapons, knights almost never do, warriors use whatever gives them the best agro most of the time. Monks may want it but I doubt any of the other melee would. Ofcourse this part could be useless for melee depending how it works with the skill caps. May allow shaman to actually hit when meleeing, it would take your 200 skill in 1hb and turn it into 240 (I think OoW changed our ckill caps but I dont recall them right now).<br />
<br />
In any event the spell is still changing.</p>
	
	
	
