	<p>Why would every group want a shaman just for the ability to give them a couple more HPs and 1H blunt? After all clerics are not wanted because they spend their time casting HP buffs - they are wanted for sheer healing power.<br />
<br />
This spell is good for raids, for grouping in high risk places like Riftseeker's and to cast on your group's melees if every single one of your damage spells gets resisted. It does not make us heal better in any form, as we do not use a tank's full HP bar anyways, not by a long shot. All this is good for is to allow a chainhealing cleric a greater margin of error.<br />
<br />
I doubt I would ever cast it in a group setting except when pulling nameds in dangerous places. I guess the removed recast timer is nice in that case though.</p>
	
	
	
